column5: I just recently got back into spinner fishing last summer and now i,am hooked.Pretty much all my good size fish the last season have been on spinners here's a preview.All but one fish were released can u guess which one? nope not the hens they go back to do their thing
very nice bro.... i am liking the spinners and jerkbaits this season too...
